{"tid":1784994,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日遊行促立港人權法","createTime":"2019-12-16T05:23:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T05:52:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5567d98887aa47146b1dd80282cd8112317d9846","tid":1784994,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:23:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191216/KNHUKGM7G6RC3GMJC7WS4NURTA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191216%2FKNHUKGM7G6RC3GMJC7WS4NURTA%2F&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hvUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=f4abf17a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191216%2FKNHUKGM7G6RC3GMJC7WS4NURTA%2F&h=306526cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191216/KNHUKGM7G6RC3GMJC7WS4NURTA/</a><br />\n<br />\n日遊行促立港人權法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191216/large/1576425933_103d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191216%2Flarge%2F1576425933_103d.jpg&h=abed8c5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n遊行人士手持標語，促請日本政府制訂日版人權法。Twitter圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】美國總統特朗普簽署人權法後，不少港人都希望各國跟隨美國步伐。有居住日本的港人昨下午在東京發起「日本萡香港人權法案竾」遊行，促請日本政府制訂日版人權法，結果有逾百人響應；除港人外，亦有日本人和在日台灣人，甚至有到日本旅遊的內地人支持。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：市民籲罷食藍店：一啖一滴細路血<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手風琴拉奏《榮光》<br />\n<br />\n有參與遊行的人士於社交媒體Twitter上載昨日遊行情況，遊行隊伍日本當地時間下午3時半，在東京日比谷公園出發。他們在遊行開始前，先為反送中運動首位不幸墮樓死亡的抗爭者梁凌杰默哀，隨後拉起寫有促請日本政府制訂人權法的橫額出發，沿途高叫「光復香港，時代革命」、「Stand with Hong Kong」，又用日語叫喊「保護香港」、「保護人權」等口號。其中一名遊行發起人表示，希望能引起日本社會對香港關注，促請日方訂立日版人權法。<br />\n<br />\n有日本人亦參與遊行，他帶着寫有「造反有理，革命無罪」、「驅逐共黨，光復香港」的標語。他認為，不同地方的政權都有不守諾言情況，故希望站出來，為香港發聲，並希望大家不要受傷；又用手風琴拉奏《願榮光歸香港》。另有在日工作的港人表示，美國簽署法案後，日本已多了政黨關注，雖然未知日本政府會否制訂法案，但作為港人亦應繼續發聲。"},{"pid":"db40cb9f7498c1f5fda2c9be88f39c896880702f","tid":1784994,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:24:15.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位推行動po<br />\n除夕夜 築人鏈<br />\n1月1 街度見<br />\n【重推-仲有冇火?】1231築人鏈 1月1日街上見！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1784122\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1784122</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ba55a8262307fb01290a9af3ea2483dc0f040db8","tid":1784994,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NnDkzda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNnDkzda.jpg&h=97bc3868&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMC8VCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMC8VCF.jpg&h=36102201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/boyz9mA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fboyz9mA.jpg&h=681d4c57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WpGueC9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWpGueC9.jpg&h=2c51b16f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24d5f02290d91531abd7159f741a2d5198530007","tid":1784994,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:29:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">請各位喺出post前貼多張日程表or文宣</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁文宣組就冇咁忙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sdw2RCH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsdw2RCH.jpg&h=8da8b8c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ja88Na2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fja88Na2.jpg&h=543efee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmRJ7hx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-s